\f3\i Alfer, Alferine
\f2\i0  - a militant animalist, or referring to such organizations. An animal-sint militant. Many factions exist. Could be anything from a violent anti-huum revolutionary to a pacifist sint-rights advocate. Don't like this term. Playing with "Untamed" instead, though it is probably (?) too derivative from Game of Thrones "unsullied", I like it.\
\

